					return "\n## Why Inspect a New Build?\n\nEven new homes can have defects. Builder warranties don't cover everything, and once the build is complete, it's harder and more expensive to fix issues. Our stage inspections help you:\n\n- **Catch defects early** when they're easier to fix\n- **Ensure building code compliance**\n- **Protect your warranty rights**\n- **Have peace of mind** throughout the build process\n\n## Recommended Inspection Stages\n\n### 1. Pre-Pour/Slab Inspection\n**Timing:** Before concrete is poured\n\n**What we check:**\n- Site preparation and excavation\n- Formwork and reinforcement\n- Termite protection measures\n- Plumbing under slab\n- Damp-proof membrane\n\n### 2. Frame Stage Inspection\n**Timing:** After frame is erected, before wall lining\n\n**What we check:**\n- Structural framing\n- Roof framing and trusses\n- Bracing and fixings\n- Window and door frames\n- Waterproofing details\n\n### 3. Lock-Up Stage Inspection\n**Timing:** Windows and doors installed, before internal fit-out\n\n**What we check:**\n- External cladding\n- Roof installation\n- Window and door sealing\n- Wet area waterproofing\n- Electrical and plumbing rough-in\n\n### 4. Pre-Handover (Practical Completion) Inspection\n**Timing:** Before final payment and handover\n\n**What we check:**\n- Overall finish quality\n- Compliance with plans\n- Defects and incomplete work\n- Fixtures and fittings\n- Final touches and details\n\n## Package Deals Available\n\nWe offer discounted packages for multiple stage inspections. Contact us to discuss your build timeline and create a custom inspection schedule.\n\n## What You'll Receive\n\n### After Each Inspection:\n- Detailed written report\n- Photographic evidence\n- List of identified issues\n- Recommendations for builder\n- Priority action items\n\n### Reports delivered within 24-48 hours\n\nThis allows you to raise concerns with your builder quickly while work is still in progress.\n\n## Work Directly With Your Builder\n\nOur reports are designed to facilitate productive conversations with your builder. We identify genuine issues while maintaining a professional, constructive tone.\n\n## Book Your Stage Inspections\n\nContact us early in your build process to schedule inspections at the right stages.\n\n**Phone:** 0438 825 008\n**Email:** info@magnumbi.com.au\n";
